## Key Files

### Backend Entry Points
- Server: `backend/server.js`
- Routes: `backend/routes/*.js`
- Controllers: `backend/controllers/*.js`
- Models: `backend/models/*.js`
- External APIs: `backend/api/*.js`
- Utilities: `backend/utils/*.js`

### Frontend Entry Points
- App: `frontend/pages/_app.js`
- API Client: `frontend/lib/api.js`
- Hooks: `frontend/lib/hooks/*.js`
- Utilities: `frontend/lib/utils/*.js`
- Components: `frontend/components/**/*.js`

## Code Patterns

### Backend Controller
```javascript
/**
 * Handler description
 * @route METHOD /api/endpoint
 * @see {@link docs/API_REFERENCE.md#section} for API docs
 */
const handler = async (req, res, next) => {
  try {
    // Implementation
    res.json({ success: true, data: {} });
  } catch (error) {
    next(error);
  }
};
```

### Frontend Component
```javascript
/**
 * Component description
 * @param {Object} props
 * @see {@link docs/frontend/components/Component.md} for docs
 */
export default function Component({ prop }) {
  // Implementation
}
```

### Test File
```javascript
/**
 * Unit tests for Module
 * @file path/to/__tests__/module.test.js
 * @see docs/path/to/doc.md for documentation
 */
describe('Module', () => {
  it('should work correctly', () => {
    // Test
  });
});
```

## Before Committing Checklist

- [ ] `npm run format` executed
- [ ] `npm test` passes
- [ ] JSDoc comments added
- [ ] Documentation updated
- [ ] Tests added for new code
- [ ] No linter errors

## Ignored Folders (Do Not Modify)

Per user rules, do not modify:
- `packages/next-infra/src/server`
- `packages/next-infra/src/webpack/mf-utils/test-server`

